subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution. Central and southern Mexico ( Chiapas , Morelos ), Guatemala ( Baja Verapaz , Zacapa ), and Honduras ( Comayagua , La Paz ). Also recorded from Guanacaste, Costa Rica in the literature (
Swift et al., 2010
), but no specimens examined in this study had labels from this locality ( Fig. 35 ).
